msgstr "La anotaciĂ³n `@RunOnVirtualThread` se puede utilizar junto con la anotaciĂ³n  link:{rm_blocking_annotation}[@Blocking] para especificar un nombre de trabajador."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.8/guides/messaging-virtual-threads.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Then, for example, to set the maximum concurrency of this method down to 30, set using the config property `smallrye.messaging.worker.my-worker.max-concurrency=30`."
